Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 吃醋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她做的菜可好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做给你吃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后给我付钱 餐费
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈美可不是你的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了别叫得那么亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动真格的 不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真气人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原话返还
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 现在得先去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 救出佳奈美然后把无常...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭揍一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天罚之
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也这么想的吧 你这家伙
